# Topic Modelling

## Interactive Topic Model Visualization

The 19 topics were clustered using a similarity measure to calculate the distance between topics and the results are presented in a two-dimensional graph using multidimensional scaling.

```{r, echo=F, warning=F, message=F, eval=T, results='hide'}
folder <- "C:/Users/User/OneDrive - PUJ Cali/PhD/6. P4_Eco-innov_review/2. Data_review"
# Load results
load(paste(folder, "/5_Topic_model_eco-innov/results_LDA_eco-innov_061221.rda", sep=""))
```

```{r, echo=F, warning=F, message=F, eval=T}
stm::toLDAvis(h3,
              docs=e4$documents,
              R = 10,
              plot.opts = list(xlab = "", ylab = ""),
              lambda.step = 1,
              out.dir = "G:/Mi unidad/Web_pages/review_paper_ecoinnov/topic_modeling_files",
              open.browser = F,
              as.gist = FALSE,
              reorder.topics = T
)
```

